DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260423T200000
UID:699761488b29ea2800d11b7c@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Adobe Lightroom Classic is an industry standard tool used by p
 hotographers to organize\, retouch\, their work. We will focus on learning
  the workflow of the software\, covering topics such as importing photos\,
  file organization\, retouching and correcting our images\, and exporting 
 and sharing our finished work.\nRegistration is required.\nInformation Col
 lection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form is collected by the
