DESCRIPTION:Piskel is a simple web-based and desktop-based software applic
 ation for the creation of still and animated pixel art. This is a basic le
 sson in drawing a walk cycle (or run cycle) involving a human (or ape).\nR
 egistration is required.\nRegistration begins April 6th\, 2026 at 12:30pm.
 \nNote: Your spot will not be guaranteed after 5 minutes of the start of t
 he program.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on t
 his form is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libra
 ries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information will only b
 e used for event and program registration\, delivery and evaluation. Quest
 ions about how the library handles your information can be directed to Ans
 werline staff at\nanswerline@tpl.ca\n\, 416-397-5981\, 789 Yonge Street\, 
 Toronto ON M4W 2G8
