SUMMARY:Youth Hub: Japanese Fruit Sandwiches
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260423T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260423T180000
UID:69bd8791ad384e40edb5b722@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Chef Yumiko Kobayashi will teach the basics of how to make a J
 apanese fruit sandwich. Participants will create the unique Asian-style sa
 ndwich using ingredients* prepared by the Chef and eat their own creations
 .\n*Food allergy notice: Please be aware that food will be used in this pr
 ogram that contains gluten and dairy. Certain food ingredients may cause a
 llergic reactions in some people. ​\nThis program is part of Youth Hub s
 ervice. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the
  summer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snac
 ks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the bran
 ch to find out more.
