DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T180000
UID:698f72153cc3e0c9ecb915c0@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Ready to level up your business game?\nIn this interactive wor
 kshop\, you’ll learn how to use social media like a pro to grow your bra
 nd and stand out online. We’ll break down the hottest platforms\, show y
 ou how to create scroll-stopping content\, and connect with your audience 
 that builds hype and loyalty.\nIf you’ve got a business idea\, this is y
 our chance to turn likes and follows into real success. Let’s unlock you
 r potential and take your hustle to the next level.\nDrop-in. Limited spot
 s.\nThis workshop is part of the Youth for Entrepreneurship program led by
  the YMCA of Greater Toronto. Through hands-on sessions\, you’ll gain th
 e digital tools\, financial knowledge\, and creative strategies needed to 
 build a business idea from the ground
LOCATION:Albert Campbell\, Auditorium (lower level)
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698f72153cc3e0c9ecb915c0
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
