UID:69c1c32fb6c4ac1fedc7b786@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Learn all about Makey-Makey!  Makey-Makey is an invention ki
 t for the 21st Century.  When the small circuit board is connected to a c
 omputer it allows users to turn everyday conductive objects\, like play do
 h\, fruit or tinfoil\, into touchpads and keyboards!\nFor kids ages 5-12 w
 ith parents or caregivers.  Registration is required.\nEach registration 
 spot is for one family. Please register once per family\n.\nInformation Co
 llection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form is collected by th
