 axy.\nRecommended Materials:\nPencil\, eraser\, sharpener\, mixed media pa
 per or watercolour paper\, black sharpie or other permanent marker\, oil p
 astels or wax crayons\, watercolours\, medium sized brush\, a little bit o
 f salt.\nZoom URL to access the online program will be emailed to registra
 nts ahead of program date.\nThis online program is suitable for children a
 ges 6-12. Younger children may require assistance from caregivers. It is r
 ecommended that parents or caregivers are present during this live program
 . Questions about online programs? Please email us at programproposals@tpl
 .ca.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on this for
 m is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libraries Ac
