DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260326T200000
UID:697ccf92377f55c8ec16951d@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:If you've ever wanted to up your photography game\, whether yo
 u just want to get better at taking pictures with your phone\, or you want
  to graduate to a professional DSLR or mirrorless camera\, join us for a c
 lass on the basics of photography. We will go over the basic settings that
  go into a good photo as well as talking about camera settings\, lenses\, 
 and lighting.\nRegistration opens 2 weeks prior to class.\nAll equipment w
 ill be provided.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information
  on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public 
 Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information will o
 nly be used for event and program registration\, delivery and evaluation. 
 Questions about how the library handles your information can be directed t
