DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260416T180000
UID:69bc3d4bad384e40edb57f89@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Teens will create their own custom keychains\nusing Cricut Des
 ign Space and the Cricut machine! Teens will design and print their own st
 ickers and decals\, which they can then transfer onto their keychain. All
  materials will be provided\; this is a drop-in program.\nThis program is 
 part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens afte
 r school and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available. Fr
 ee\, nutritious snacks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth 
 Hub\nor call the branch to find out more.
