DESCRIPTION:Snap It! The Science Club is an exciting learning program wher
 e kids become young engineers. With Snap Circuits\, they build real electr
 onic circuits and learn basic science concepts in an easy\, creative\, and
  playful way.\nLimited to 10 participants.\nPlease arrive early to secure 
