DESCRIPTION:Unleash your creativity as you design your own stunning nail a
 rt! Join us for one or all of our fabulous Nail Nights on the first Monday
  of every month. Drop-in\, no registration required.\nThis program is par
 t of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after s
 chool and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free\
 , nutritious snacks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub
 \nor call the branch to find out more.
LOCATION:S. Walter Stewart\, Auditorium
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6942f4eb6f926136000b6c87
