DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260424T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260424T110000
UID:699de4fbb0595799c09f0e65@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Participants will have access to individualized one-to-one emp
 loyment support sessions. These sessions provide personalized guidance tai
 lored to each participant’s career goals\, including resume and cover le
 tter review\, job search planning\, interview preparation\, and referrals 
 to additional employment and community resources. The one-to-one format en
 sures participants receive targeted coaching and practical next steps to s
 upport their employment journey. These workshops are co-sponsored with Acc
 ess Employment.\nRegistration required. Each booking is for 30 minutes. Pl
 ease register for the timeslot that suits your availability.\nInformation 
 Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form is collected by 
 the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)
 \, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information will only be used for event and prog
 ram registration\, delivery and evaluation. Questions about how the librar
 y handles your information can be directed to Answerline staff at\nanswerl
 ine@tpl.ca\n\, 416-397-5981\, 789 Yonge Street\, Toronto ON M4W 2G8.
LOCATION:Goldhawk Park
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/699de4fbb0595799c09f0e65
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
