BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Vegetarian Sushi Making Workshop with Chef Sang Kim
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260514T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260514T170000
UID:69bd4d91db57df044296f36d@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:TV host and celebrity Chef Sang Kim will teach the basics of s
 ushi making. Participants will make sushi rolls using ingredients prepared
  by the Chef and eat their own creations. A brief history of sushi\, its o
 rigins and eating etiquette will also be shared. Prizes are also awarded f
 or best sushi creations.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal inf
 ormation on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the
  Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The informatio
 n will only be used for event and program registration\, delivery and eval
 uation. Questions about how the library handles your information can be di
