 of the newest tricks in the world of magic. Participants will also get a c
 hance to learn some simple\, yet astonishing magic tricks using everyday o
 bjects.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welco
 ming place for teens after school and in the summer\, where helpful staff 
