  award-winning creator of\nJellaby\n! Kean will lead you through the foun
 dations of creating fun\, compelling characters\, plot outlines\, and pull
 ing it all together by laying out and drawing your own comic!\nThis progra
 m is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens
  after school and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available
 . Free\, nutritious snacks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nY
 outh Hub\nor call the branch to find out more.
