DESCRIPTION:Join us for small group visits with a therapy dog! Children wi
 ll have an opportunity to read\, listen to stories and engage in therapeut
 ic human-animal interaction. This free program is presented in partnership
  with One Health Partners. Suitable for school-aged children aged 5-12.\nP
 lease Note: A maximum of 5 children can participate in the program during 
